                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-970-18591024 t18591024-970-punishment-75"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">MALLET</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18591024-970-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18591024-970-verdict-2" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18591024-970-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to. mercy by the Jury on account of his character.—
